quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,88,"Jilani: “Ana ni nduni jwamuli munkono Mwakwe mwana Umwenye wachilichose, soni Jwalakwe ni jwaakugosa (indu yosope) nambo pangali champaka chigosedwe pa ilagasyo Yakwe, nam’baga jenumanja ŵakumanyililaga?”"
  23,89,"(Pakwanga) tajile: “Allah.” Jilani: “Nambi mkulojedwa chinauli?”"
  23,90,"Nambo twaichilile ni yakuona, nambo soni chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaunami."
  25,34,"Aŵala ŵatachisonganganyisidwa (alinkuutidwa) chamakuku wa ku Jahannama, ŵanganyao ni ŵatachiŵa pamalo pakusakala nnope, nambo soni ni ŵakusokonechela nnope kwitala (lyagoloka)."
  25,35,"Soni chisimu pamasile patwampele Musa Chitabu (Taurat), ni twam’bichile nkulugwe Haruna kuŵa nkunkamuchisya."
  25,36,"Ni twatite: “Jawulani ŵanaŵaŵilimmwe ku ŵandu aŵala ŵaayikaaniile isimosimo Yetu.” Basi ni twajonasile kusyene (panyuma pakwakanila achimitengao)."
  26,7,"Ana nganaliona litaka – kuti mmela ulingwa watuumesisye mwalakwemo wa ntundu uliose wakusalala chenene?"
  26,8,"Chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana chilosyo (cha ukombosi wa Allah), nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila."
  26,9,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu, ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope."